{"tid":1421144,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[脱港獨帽子] 光復香港，時代革正","createTime":"2019-08-06T07:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T18:59:24.000Z","uid":153087,"like":4,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fd5b18f4565d19c3c84e62151489039ba2e2a22e","tid":1421144,"uid":153087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:09:15.000Z","msg":"不得不承認港獨仲未係大部份人認同。由反送中到五六七大訴求亦與港獨無關，「革命」二字被港共淋奠扣上港獨帽子，暗示我地想武裝革命起義，實無可口非。<br />\n如其比人誤會，或每次比人扣帽都要解釋一輪，不如改少少。我覺得革正意思更貼近五大訴求，叫起上黎都高音啲。<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？有冇其他建議？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n革正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n革命就革命，搞真革命起義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3daf3227aab73dedb1192233ad274dfb4807ad42","tid":1421144,"uid":153087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:11:48.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7d0f8e004a7c4310dbe36c66bc6532404cbe567f","tid":1421144,"uid":153087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:13:36.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"bad5f2febea3680e03c89f036e6872b1426c1d27","tid":1421144,"uid":259882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:13:57.000Z","msg":"愛國愛港 反黑反暴"},{"pid":"482f77ba60e06b697fe4d04cc4a0b79dc844a15a","tid":1421144,"uid":268809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:14:30.000Z","msg":"光復香港 = 真正落實一國兩制, 港人治港, 實行雙普選 (家陣係西環治港)<br />\n時代革命 = 改革制度, 落實雙普選<br />\n咁解讀得唔得?"},{"pid":"b67d83fe9f0e558cf50daafc8a9ad076caef3886","tid":1421144,"uid":153087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:17:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d4bfc38910d01a9e3f4f47ee9c93f569d86da3f8","tid":1421144,"uid":245484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:22:16.000Z","msg":"食催淚蛋當落胡椒粉<br />\n橡膠彈海棉彈當打war game咁又係硬食<br />\n一棍棍比狗扑，一刀刀比黑社會斬<br />\n<br />\n呢個情況同我地講，我地要驚嗌句口號呀？唔係咁搞笑呀？<br />\n叫個冷氣軍師劉細良死撚開啦"},{"pid":"af83f1fd5afaba5caf772f224bc2b7579e5f9ba7","tid